        "body": "This is an idea I had. The Ardite schemas was initially inspired by JSON schema, but what we are _really_ doing is letting the user define a type system, not a data schema.\n\nMaybe we should rethink our terminology and approach to schema? I'm thinking most of the code stays the same, but maybe things get renamed.\n"
